   <div class="content-inner col-md-9 col-sm-9">
    <h1>
     The Write Attitude
    </h1>
    <h3>
     Employers Seek Strong Writers. Will You Be Ready?
    </h3>
    <p>
     The
     <em>
      New York Times
     </em>
     reported that in response to the question "What skills do entry level job seekers lack the most?" Human Resources executives overwhelmingly reported "written communication" as the largest deficiency (45%). To learn more about the connection between effective writing skills and career opportunities, click
     <a href="http://www.aacu.org/leap/documents/2013_EmployerSurvey.pdf" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
      here
     </a>
     .
    </p>
    <h2>
     <strong>
      Savannah State University's Quality Enhancement Plan Impact Report (2011-2016) | SACSCOC Fifth-Year Interim Report
     </strong>
    </h2>
    <p>
     Savannah State University submitted its first
     <a href="savannahstate/files/37/37246809-8800-43d0-b685-4e1d9001f290.pdf" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
      QEP Impact Report
     </a>
     in March 2017.
    </p>
    <h2>
     The Write Attitude has a new TV commercial!
     <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MjVWelkoYmw" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: 20px;" target="_blank">
      Check it out
     </a>
     <span style="color: #222222; font-size: 20px;">
      !
     </span>
    </h2>
    <p>
     Produced by the
     <a href="About-QEP/QEP-Team.shtml" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
      QEP Team
     </a>
     and
     <a href="http://www.tigersroar.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
      The Tiger's Roar TV
     </a>
     . Script written by SSU student Sierra Walton. Starring SSU students Joshua Cliatt and Sierra Walton.
    </p>
    <h2>
     <strong style="color: #222222; font-size: 20px; line-height: 22px;">
      Visit our Before I Die Wall:
      <a href="http://beforeidie.city/walls/savannah-ga/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
       http://beforeidie.city/walls/savannah-ga/
      </a>
     </strong>
    </h2>
    <h2>
     <a href="http://beforeidie.city/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
      <em style="font-size: 12px;">
       Before I Die
      </em>
     </a>
     <span style="font-size: 12px; color: #555555;">
      is a global art project that invites people to reflect on their lives and share their personal aspirations in public space. This project was started by Candy Chang on an abandoned house in New Orleans after she lost someone she loved.
     </span>
    </h2>
   </div>
